sellerAgent.name: Helen Vinson Oracle Land and Home

data.description: Seller will accept or counter offers between $250,000 and $270,000. Wonderful updated 2 bedroom 2 bath home located in the beautiful & cooler town of Oracle. Home includes newer laminate flooring, newer HVAC system, updated kitchen with newer cabinets, Corian countertops and stainless-steel appliances.  Additional rooms can be used for a playroom, storage, and office.  Large pantry/storage/laundry room, which includes the washer and dryer.  Huge and beautiful backyard with citrus and nut trees, large storage shed, flagstone patio and new cedar wood fence surrounding the entire backyard.  This home is perfect for people who want to live away from the city but still have all the amenities of shopping & entertainment close by.
